    <p class="book-lede">Build your skills in promo and trailer reads; script breakdown; and career strategy. Pick a time below — sessions are 60 minutes, $200, paid at booking.</p>
    <p class="book-cred">Jack is a regular teacher at <em>SAG-AFTRA at the Don LaFontaine VO Lab</em>, and teams with industry icons like Marie Westbrook and Brian Lee in collaborative workshops.</p>

